(79627, 0, 1, 0, 'I\'ll be your eyes and ears here in Talador, commander.', 38556), -- 79627
(81076, 0, 0, 0, 'In my days as a rangari I have hunted and been hunted by more things than I care to count. It is my hope that I can impart some of my knowledge to you without you having to experience all of these horrible things.', 38556), -- 81076
